sellerCard.description:
At Icon Pro Solutions, we specialize in transforming ideas into impactful digital experiences. With a talented team of designers, developers, and business development specialists, we offer comprehensive solutions from strategic branding to cutting-edge web development and results-driven marketing strategies. 

Our portfolio spans various industries, showcasing our ability to adapt and excel. Our approach combines creativity with data-driven insights, ensuring tailored solutions that meet our clients' goals. Let us help you navigate the digital landscape and achieve sustainable growth.

description.content:
Are you Struggling to set up your Professional Business Website or WordPress blog?

 

WE'RE HERE TO MAKE YOUR LIFE EASY!

 

I'm a Fiverr Best Seller and an experienced Engineer with over 3000+ reviews on different platforms & 10+ years dedicated to the Fiverr Platform. WordPress can provide you with the professional and customized tools that you need in the ever-so-demanding world of IT, where I deliver my work with the assurance and accuracy of an engineer's experience. Me and my team design and develops professional WordPress sites and web apps for you, on a tight budget.

 

Why Us?

  1. Goal-oriented WordPress Solutions
  2. Professional Responsive Design: Stunning on all devices
  3. Dedicated Consultation: Personalized prototype before development
  4. Wide Portfolio: e-commerce, real estate, courses, memberships...

 

Workflow

  • Briefing & Problem Analysis
  • Consulting on a Customized Solution
  • Wireframing & Prototyping (premium)
  • Execution


Mobile Friendly layout | Conventional SEO | Optimized Google rankings | Social media integration, Security | Analytics


*Package Updated on 12 Feb 2024 to include Web Prototype.


P.S. Contact me before placing an order; I might have a special coupon ready for you!

questionsAndAnswers.question: I am ready to place order, What do you need from me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If you are going to place basic order then i need your Wordpress theme & login info I have already mentioned it on my GIG page also, & if you are going to order Standard or Premium then I need your content too which includes images & text, you want to add in website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you create Custom Website or Blog?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I can do a fully custom website or blog for you, You have to contact with me to discuss with details.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide hosting/domain name registration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well both yes and no,Its recommended to buy your own hosting before getting a designer to work with it,but many times people are either confused or buy hosts which are really expensive and they don't really need them. We have different promo-codes with companies like hostgator we can help you with.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website easily? I know just Basics.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, very easily. I'll be sure to help you out through the process of understanding the basics of the site. Remember, we;re in this together. :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you fluent in English?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Well YEAH, When I was doing my Engineering I particiated and won in National & International Debating Competitons. I have a 8.5/9.0 Band score in ILETS of British Counsil and am regularly invited in International Conferences, So I'd like to think So :D

Waqar and his team are truly an incredible group of designers. 
I couldn't recommend them enough and I will absolutely be hiring them again for any additional websites that I will need down the line.
10 out of 10 very satisfied!

Phenomenal and timely work!

The website turned out great, I am very happy.

Waqar with Icon Pro Solutions has been nothing short of FANTASTIC!! He and his team has been amazing and gone above and beyond helping me with copy and images. I would highly recommend him and personally am already hiring him for other projects!!
